data.title: Good Fried Chicken in Nampa
data.text: The  food is good. I like the Extra crispy chicken over the original receipt. The chicken strips are very good. I also like the chicken bowl. my only issue is sometimes the chicken has been sitting for a while and tuffins up a bit.

data.title: Greeeeeeeeeeeeeeesy! Not my idea of fried chicken!
data.text: Sharing the same building as A&W, this fried chicken establishment is always out of what I want. My favorite KFC has always been original recipe. Still, it's probably for the best. Even when they have what I want, it's always overly greasy. The potatoes are instant and the gravy seems "plastic-y". They don't even give you real butter for your biscuit and even the honey isn't really honey. It's a high-fructose substitute. The last time I ate there was the LAST time I'll eat there.
